Spec: CLI Command Handlers
Purpose:
  Provide shared constraints for SpecDD CLI command handler modules.

Structure:
  ./commands.sdd: Shared command handler specification.
  ./*.sdd: Command-specific specifications.
  ./*.ts: Command handler implementations.
  ./*.test.ts: Command handler tests.

Owns:
  ./commands.sdd
  command handler conventions

References:
  ../container.sdd

Must:
  Expose command factories that return commander @Command instances.
  Receive command dependencies through command-specific container objects.
  Describe command arguments and options in help output.
  Set concise command descriptions for help output.
  Include the project copyright notice in help output.
  Include SpecDD framework and CLI project help links in help output.
  Expose factories suitable for @Container wiring.

Must not:
  Construct application services.
  Implement the CLI entrypoint.

Depends on:
  commander
  @Container
